List of used libraries:

OpenCV >= 2.3	(image analyse)
libfreenect (kinect driver)
libonion		(webserver)
libboost (for signal functionality)
oscpack (OSC implementation)
libjpeg8 or libpng

=======

List of packages (Ubuntu)

sudo apt-get install \
libfreenect-dev \
liblo-dev libboost-signals-dev libboost-regex-dev libboost-system-dev \
libpng-dev libjpeg-turbo8-dev \
opencv-core2.3 opencv-core-dev opencv-highgui2.3 opencv-highgui-dev \
libopencv-gpu-dev libopencv-contrib-dev libopencv-contrib2.3 \
libhighgui-dev libcv-dev

